										p.about-us__slide-text Today, Russian Standard Vodka’s brands – Original, Platinum, Gold and IMPERIA – dominate the premium vodka segment in Russia and are exported to more than 80 markets around the world. Russian Standard Vodka is Russia’s only truly global consumer brand.
